node.text: Join us on November 10th at 3pm EST to hear four experts discuss TikTok and IG Reels. Rachael Cihlar, VP Center of Excellence at @mavrckco , and Toria Roth, Social Media Marketing Specialist at @crocs will be joined by creators @jugglinjosh and @sweetportfolio to dig into the details and help brand marketers navigate the short-form video content space. Register with the link in our bio!
